''Staves of the adder'' could be found in possession of agents of Zhentarim in Zhentil Keep.

Priests worshiping the god Vaerae, also known as [[Sseth]], carried the ''staves of the serpent''.

Beyond the world of [[Toril]], ''staves of the adder'' could be found on the world of [[Aebrynis]]<ref>{{Cite book| author = Wolfgang Baur| title = Warlock of the Stonecrows| short_story = | date = | editor = Dan Wenger| publisher = TSR, Inc.| ISBN = 0-7869-0185-3| pages = 39| chapter = }} and in the [[Domains of Dread]], Nova Vassa and Har'Akir<ref>{{Cite book| author = Bruce Nesrnith| title = Touch of Death| short_story = | date = | editor = Caroline Spector| publisher = TSR, Inc.| ISBN = 1-56076-144-X| pages = 29| chapter = }}, where the staves were called the ''staves of [[Set]]'' and wielded by his clerics.<ref>{{Cite book| author = Lisa Smedman| title = The Awakening| short_story = | date = | editor = Richard Pike-Brown| publisher = TSR, Inc.| ISBN = 1-56076-883-5| pages = 23| chapter = }}
